  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figure or VFR chart ED(4) from GSPRM 2017. <br>While planning a day VFR flight between Freistadt aerodrome LOLF (N48\u00b031', E014\u00b025') to Dingolfing aerodrome EDPD (N48\u00b040', E012\u00b030'), you need to select visually conspicuous point for the sector West of the E013\u00b045' to record the progress of the flight. Which of the following is the best waypoint?</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "The mast at N48\u00b032', E013\u00b036'.",
    "b": "The motorway bridge at N48\u00b036', E13\u00b022'.",
    "c": "The lighted mass at N48\u00b047', E012\u00b053'.",
    "d": "Vilshofen aerodrome (EDMV) at N48\u00b038', E013\u00b012'."
  },
  "correctOption": "b",
